title: The Mike Rosen Radio Show JAN-03-2013 FRI
description:
The Mike Rosen Radio Show JAN-03-2013 FRI............PODCAST



Friday, January 03, 2014
Movie Review Double Feature

 
 

 - 9AM Hour

1. Network reporting on ship stuck in ice fails to mention
          it was on a climate change observation mission. 
2. MSNBC personal attacks are beyond the pale. 
3. Discussion of girl who went into coma following tonsillectomy.



 - 10AM hour

1. Guest: Jon Caldara, President of the Independence Institute 
      Voter registration controversy. 
2. Price fluctuations on the price of marijuana in Colorado.
3. Michael Moore criticizes Obamacare because it doesn't go far enough.
        He wants a single payer system.



 - 11AM Hour

Movie Review, Mike and Christian Toto review 
                 Saving Mr. Banks and American Hustle.

 Be sure to follow Christian on his blog: http://daddylibrium.com/
